     H            Y.                                    1
     F** AIARC7 **********************************
     F*       ..ＡＰＩＣＳ通信システム..       *
     F*            <<ASCII--->EBCDIC>>           *
     F*  CODING:A.INOUE           2004.08.09     *
     F************************ COPY FROM AIARCV **
     FINPUT   IP  F     256            DISK
     FOUTPUT  O   F    1024            DISK
     E                    IBUFF    5000  1
     E                    OBUFF    8000  1
     E                    OUTDT    1024  1
     IINPUT   AA  01
     I                                        1 256 DATA
     IPBUFF       DS
     I                                        15000 IBUFF
     IDSBUFF      DS
     I                                        18000 OBUFF
     I            DS
     I                                        11024 OUTDT
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           CTYPE   2
      *
     C                     Z-ADD0         PDBCS   50
     C                     Z-ADD1024      PBLEN   50
     C                     MOVELDATA      PBUFF
     C                     EXSR #CVT
     C                     MOVEADSBUFF    OUTDT
     C                     BITOF'01234567'HEX1    1        X'0D'
     C                     BITON'457'     HEX1
     C                     BITOF'01234567'HEX2    1        X'0A'
     C                     BITON'46'      HEX2
     C                     EXCPTDAT
      *-----------------------------------------------------*
     C           #CVT      BEGSR
     C                     MOVE CTYPE     PTYPE   2
     C                     MOVE 'N'       PSISO   1
     C                     CALL 'CVTR00'
     C                     PARM           PTYPE
     C                     PARM           PBLEN
     C                     PARM           PBUFF
     C                     PARM           PSISO
     C                     PARM           PDBCS
     C                     PARM           DSBUFF
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    PBUFF
     C                     ENDSR
     OOUTPUT  E                DAT
     O                         OUTDT   1024
     O**                       HEX1      21
     O**                       HEX2      22
